        <item>
          <title>Baseball legend Pete Rose dies at 83</title>
          <description><![CDATA[(KRON) -- Baseball legend Pete Rose died Monday at the age of 83. Rose's complicated legacy includes being MLB's all-time hits leader but being banned from the league for gambling on games. He died Monday morning in his Las Vegas home, TMZ said. The outlet did not reveal a cause of death.]]></description>
